<div id="for-families" class="for-families">For Families:</div>

<div>We rate and review thousands of movies, TV shows, books, video games, apps, and websites according to developmental-criteria recommendations from some of the nation&#39;s leading authorities. In short, we review everything you and your family wants to or will be watching, playing, reading, or surfing. Here&#39;s how to understand <a href="https://www.commonsensemedia.org/about-us/our-mission/about-our-ratings">our ratings</a>.</div>

