</ul>
</div>

<div class="for-educators">
<p>For Educators:</p>

<p>Editors consider the following factors when deciding to review a tool:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Requests from educators</li>
	<li>Breadth of coverage across subjects, grade bands, and platforms</li>
	<li>Popular and trending tools</li>
	<li>Editorial interests</li>
</ul>
</div>

<div class="understand">
<p>Here&#39;s how to understand <a href="https://www.commonsense.org/education/how-we-rate-and-review">our ratings</a>.</p>

